  ('dietitian-moex-04109', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關gluconeogenesis之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["Cori cycle中，gluconeogenesis發生於肌肉組織", "acetyl-CoA是pyruvate carboxylase的調節因子", "glycerol、lactate與ethanol可作為gluconeogenesis的前驅物", "oxaloacetate可穿透粒線體膜，在細胞質中經phosphoenolpyruvate carboxykinase催化轉變成 phosphoenolpyruvate"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6711d3d5b971", "answer_pdf_sha1": "97790a8d5dc0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04110', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '哺乳動物進行糖質新生反應時，利用丙酮酸羧化酶（pyruvate carboxylase）催化丙酮酸合成草醯 醋酸（oxaloacetate），此酵素需要何種輔酵素參與？', '["核黃素腺嘌呤二核苷酸（flavin adenine dinucleotide, FAD）", "生物素（biotin）", "硫胺素焦磷酸（thiamin pyrophosphate, TPP）", "鈷胺素（cobalamin）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6711d3d5b971", "answer_pdf_sha1": "97790a8d5dc0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04111', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '人體於飲食攝取葡萄糖後的兩小時內，在各組織中的葡萄糖利用，下列何者錯誤？', '["在腦部可被氧化而產生ATP", "在紅血球可進入糖解作用", "在脂肪組織可成為合成三酸甘油酯的原料", "在肝臟優先進入脂肪酸合成途徑"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6711d3d5b971", "answer_pdf_sha1": "97790a8d5dc0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04112', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關脂肪酸進行氧化作用的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["脂肪酸為高活化能分子，需換成較低活化能的fatty acyl-CoA始能進入粒線體", "脂肪酸透過fatty acyl-CoA synthetase可轉換成fatty acyl-CoA，轉換過程需要ATP分子", "fatty acyl-CoA經由carnitine acyltransferase和肉鹼（carnitine）結合能進入粒線體間膜進行 氧化", "carnitine acyltransferase為脂肪酸分解的速率關鍵酵素，會受到acetyl-CoA回饋抑制"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6711d3d5b971", "answer_pdf_sha1": "97790a8d5dc0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04113', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關人體合成及利用酮體（ketone bodies）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["肝臟細胞的細胞質為合成酮體的場所，所產生酮體再運送至肝外組織作能量來源", "酮體合成材料是acetyl-CoA和malonyl-CoA，生成的中間產物為3-hydroxy-3-methylglutaryl-CoA （HMG-CoA）", "人體產生的酮體包括 acetone、acetoacetate、β-hydroxylmethylbutyrate", "酮體運送至肝外組織後會分解為acetyl-CoA而進入檸檬酸循環"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6711d3d5b971", "answer_pdf_sha1": "97790a8d5dc0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
